{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01CyEt4rwVbTwFMQA8qkuUNb","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n     2→<web-app\n     3→    xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n     4→    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n     5→    xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n     6→    version=\"6.0\">\n     7→  <context-param>\n     8→    <param-name>jakarta.faces.PROJECT_STAGE</param-name>\n     9→    <param-value>Development</param-value>\n    10→  </context-param>\n    11→  <context-param>\n    12→    <param-name>jakarta.faces.CLIENT_WINDOW_MODE</param-name>\n    13→    <param-value>url</param-value>\n    14→  </context-param>\n    15→  <context-param>\n    16→    <param-name>primefaces.THEME</param-name>\n    17→    <param-value>saga</param-value>\n    18→  </context-param>\n    19→  <context-param>\n    20→    <param-name>primefaces.FONT_AWESOME</param-name>\n    21→    <param-value>true</param-value>\n    22→  </context-param>\n    23→  <context-param>\n    24→    <param-name>primefaces.MOVE_SCRIPTS_TO_BOTTOM</param-name>\n    25→    <param-value>true</param-value>\n    26→  </context-param>\n    27→  <mime-mapping>\n    28→    <extension>ttf</extension>\n    29→    <mime-type>application/font-sfnt</mime-type>\n    30→  </mime-mapping>\n    31→  <mime-mapping>\n    32→    <extension>woff</extension>\n    33→    <mime-type>application/font-woff</mime-type>\n    34→  </mime-mapping>\n    35→  <mime-mapping>\n    36→    <extension>woff2</extension>\n    37→    <mime-type>application/font-woff2</mime-type>\n    38→  </mime-mapping>\n    39→  <mime-mapping>\n    40→    <extension>eot</extension>\n    41→    <mime-type>application/vnd.ms-fontobject</mime-type>\n    42→  </mime-mapping>\n    43→  <servlet>\n    44→    <servlet-name>Faces Servlet</servlet-name>\n    45→    <servlet-class>jakarta.faces.webapp.FacesServlet</servlet-class>\n    46→    <load-on-startup>1</load-on-startup>\n    47→  </servlet>\n    48→  <servlet-mapping>\n    49→    <servlet-name>Faces Servlet</servlet-name>\n    50→    <url-pattern>*.xhtml</url-pattern>\n    51→  </servlet-mapping>\n    52→  <welcome-file-list>\n    53→    <welcome-file>index.xhtml</welcome-file>\n    54→    <welcome-file>index.html</welcome-file>\n    55→  </welcome-file-list>\n    56→</web-app>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"980f902c-749f-4758-bd3d-b564b09c767f"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BkQMDTvj1WPEUM5MsrMkTN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I now have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me update my plan and start the migration. The key Quarkus-specific elements to migrate are:\n\n1. **PanacheRepositoryBase** → Standard JPA with EntityManager\n2. **`@Startup` / `@UnlessBuildProfile`** → Standard CDI `@Observes` lifecycle events\n3. **`@Scheduled`** → `@Schedule` from Jakarta EE Batch/Timer\n4. **`StartupEvent` / `ShutdownEvent`** → CDI `@Observes @Initialized/@Destroyed` or `@PostConstruct`/`@PreDestroy`\n5. **`@ConfigProperty`** (MicroProfile) → Keep or use resource injection\n6. **`@QuarkusTest`** → Standard test framework\n7. **Quarkus Maven plugin** → Standard Jakarta EE app server (WildFly/Open Liberty)\n8. **`quarkus-qpid-jms`** → Direct Qpid JMS client\n9. **`application.properties`** → server configuration files\n\nFor the target runtime, I'll use **WildFly** as it's the most commonly adopted Jakarta EE application server and has excellent support for all the technologies used (CDI, JPA, JMS, JSF/PrimeFaces, JAX-RS, Batch)."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1320,"cache_read_input_tokens":85480,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1320,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":788},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"f9d96721-bfb7-4219-a546-a7700c0a7d2c"}
