{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01G2qwrvR9G7LXZ63xRXuacu","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All tasks have been completed successfully. Here's a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Configuration Files Created for Jakarta EE / WildFly Migration\n\nAll configuration files have been successfully created and organized for the Jakarta EE / WildFly migration. Here's what was accomplished:\n\n### 1. **persistence.xml** \nCreated at: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n\n- Configured with Jakarta EE persistence 3.0\n- JTA data source: `java:jboss/datasources/CargoTrackerDS`\n- Hibernate settings for schema management (create-drop)\n- SQL logging enabled\n- SQL load script configured to use `import.sql`\n\n### 2. **beans.xml**\nCreated at: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml`\n\n- Jakarta EE CDI 4.0 configuration\n- Bean discovery mode set to \"all\"\n\n### 3. **web.xml** (Moved)\nCreated at: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml`\n\n- Moved from `src/main/resources/META-INF/web.xml` to standard webapp location\n- Contains Jakarta Faces servlet configuration\n- PrimeFaces theme and configuration settings\n- Font MIME type mappings\n\n### 4. **faces-config.xml** (Moved)\nCreated at: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml`\n\n- Moved from `src/main/resources/META-INF/faces-config.xml` to standard webapp location\n- PrimeFaces dialog handlers configured\n\n### 5. **Web Resources** (Copied)\nCopied from: `src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/*`\nTo: `src/main/webapp/`\n\nAll web resources including:\n- `admin/` directory\n- `booking/` directory\n- `event-logger/` directory\n- `public/` directory\n- `resources/` directory\n- `index.xhtml`\n- `WEB-INF/templates/` directory\n\n### 6. **wildfly-config.cli**\nCreated at: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/wildfly-config.cli`\n\nWildFly CLI configuration script containing:\n- H2 datasource configuration: `CargoTrackerDS`\n- Five JMS queues:\n  - `CargoHandledQueue`\n  - `DeliveredCargoQueue`\n  - `HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptQueue`\n  - `MisdirectedCargoQueue`\n  - `RejectedRegistrationAttemptsQueue`\n\n### 7. **application.properties** (Updated)\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/resources/application.properties`\n\n- Replaced Quarkus-specific configuration with minimal Jakarta EE configuration\n- Contains only the GraphTraversalUrl property\n\n### 8. **import.sql** (Verified)\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/resources/import.sql`\n\n- Remains unchanged with the ApplicationSettings initialization\n\nThe migration is now complete with all configuration files properly structured for Jakarta EE / WildFly deployment."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"d2318230-17a3-4cf5-9241-7eabe7c689d4"}
