{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Fwz58qpJRjmkKQmwFvb5ed","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01QSrnX96oXFj42qb2ZtqEik","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix CDI injection issues","prompt":"There are deployment errors in a WildFly Jakarta EE application. I need you to fix multiple files in:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nThe errors are:\n1. `ConnectionFactory` is `@Inject`ed but needs `@Resource` for JNDI lookup\n2. `EntityManager` is `@Inject`ed in some places but should use `@PersistenceContext`\n\nFor each file, READ IT FIRST, then EDIT IT.\n\n## Files to check and fix:\n\n### 1. JmsApplicationEvents.java\nPath: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java\n- Change `@Inject private ConnectionFactory connectionFactory;` to `@Resource(lookup = \"java:/ConnectionFactory\") private ConnectionFactory connectionFactory;`\n\n### 2. InitLoader.java\nPath: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/InitLoader.java\n- Change `@Inject private EntityManager entityManager;` to `@PersistenceContext private EntityManager entityManager;`\n- Make sure the import for `jakarta.persistence.PersistenceContext` is there\n\n### 3. Check ALL remaining JMS consumer files for any `@Inject private ConnectionFactory` that needs to be `@Resource`:\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java\n\nIf they have ConnectionFactory injected with @Inject, change it to @Resource.\n\n### 4. Check ALL remaining files that might @Inject EntityManager and change to @PersistenceContext:\nUse grep to find: @Inject.*EntityManager across the entire src directory.\n\n### 5. Also search for `@Inject.*FacesContext` which also needs a CDI producer or @Inject approach. In Jakarta EE/WildFly, FacesContext is not injectable by default with CDI. Check:\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/mobile/EventLogger.java - if it has @Inject FacesContext, need to create a CDI producer or use FacesContext.getCurrentInstance() instead.\n\n### 6. Also check the test data generator files:\n- src/test/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/TestDataGenerator.java - check for @Inject EntityManager\n\nRead and fix all files. Report back what you changed.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":498,"cache_read_input_tokens":131337,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":498,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":844},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"a156d236-4e9e-4b41-9f1e-1a9e3d5e7a38"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There are deployment errors in a WildFly Jakarta EE application. I need you to fix multiple files in:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nThe errors are:\n1. `ConnectionFactory` is `@Inject`ed but needs `@Resource` for JNDI lookup\n2. `EntityManager` is `@Inject`ed in some places but should use `@PersistenceContext`\n\nFor each file, READ IT FIRST, then EDIT IT.\n\n## Files to check and fix:\n\n### 1. JmsApplicationEvents.java\nPath: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java\n- Change `@Inject private ConnectionFactory connectionFactory;` to `@Resource(lookup = \"java:/ConnectionFactory\") private ConnectionFactory connectionFactory;`\n\n### 2. InitLoader.java\nPath: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/InitLoader.java\n- Change `@Inject private EntityManager entityManager;` to `@PersistenceContext private EntityManager entityManager;`\n- Make sure the import for `jakarta.persistence.PersistenceContext` is there\n\n### 3. Check ALL remaining JMS consumer files for any `@Inject private ConnectionFactory` that needs to be `@Resource`:\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java\n\nIf they have ConnectionFactory injected with @Inject, change it to @Resource.\n\n### 4. Check ALL remaining files that might @Inject EntityManager and change to @PersistenceContext:\nUse grep to find: @Inject.*EntityManager across the entire src directory.\n\n### 5. Also search for `@Inject.*FacesContext` which also needs a CDI producer or @Inject approach. In Jakarta EE/WildFly, FacesContext is not injectable by default with CDI. Check:\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/mobile/EventLogger.java - if it has @Inject FacesContext, need to create a CDI producer or use FacesContext.getCurrentInstance() instead.\n\n### 6. Also check the test data generator files:\n- src/test/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/TestDataGenerator.java - check for @Inject EntityManager\n\nRead and fix all files. Report back what you changed."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01QSrnX96oXFj42qb2ZtqEik","session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"b656edf8-313c-43fa-b015-dba0caee6d92"}
