{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_012bfHJboN8XP4enu9Vfrr1q","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"WildFly started successfully (`WFLYSRV0025: WildFly Full 31.0.1.Final started in 10353ms - Started 639 of 839 services`). The deployment succeeded (`WFLYSRV0010: Deployed \"cargo-tracker.war\"`). \n\nThe lazy initialization error is a runtime issue when accessing pages - the Cargo entity has lazy-loaded collections that need to be fetched eagerly or within a transaction. Let me fix the Cargo entity's `Itinerary` fetch strategy and also update the `listAll()` query to use fetch joins:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1923,"cache_read_input_tokens":149076,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1923,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":264},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"74cd9672-608d-490b-9227-de289ce77dc9"}
