{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VjkwNG9p9mdDqbzxhAmeM7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's the migration summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Jakarta EE (WildFly 31)\n\n### Results\n- **All 6 smoke tests passed** against the running WildFly container\n- **WildFly 31.0.1.Final** starts in ~10 seconds and deploys the WAR successfully\n- **639 services** started, including all 5 MDBs, JPA, JSF (Mojarra 4.0.5), PrimeFaces 13.0.8, RESTEasy\n\n### Key Changes Made in This Session\n1. **Fixed `FetchType.EAGER`** on `Itinerary.java` and `Schedule.java` `@OneToMany` annotations to resolve `LazyInitializationException`\n2. **Removed `@Transactional`** from `UploadDirectoryScanner.java` (invalid on EJB `@Singleton` beans)\n3. **Fixed Dockerfile** - Added `ENTRYPOINT []` to reset the base image's Open Liberty entrypoint, and switched to JSON-form CMD for WildFly\n\n### Errors Resolved (Total: 10)\nAll errors from compilation through runtime were identified, diagnosed, and fixed iteratively:\n- Dependency issues (Jackson, ConnectionFactory, EntityManager, FacesContext)\n- JPA lazy loading (2 `@OneToMany` collections)\n- EJB annotation conflict (`@Transactional` on `@Singleton`)\n- Docker entrypoint override (Open Liberty vs WildFly)\n- WildFly CLI configuration issues (H2 driver, password)\n\n### Documentation\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md` including all files changed, errors encountered, and resolutions."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":559,"cache_read_input_tokens":66864,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":559,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":412},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","uuid":"8b7c7d5c-e9a5-401f-8d09-365f543f9b29"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2389958,"duration_api_ms":1952873,"num_turns":154,"result":"All tasks are complete. Here's the migration summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Jakarta EE (WildFly 31)\n\n### Results\n- **All 6 smoke tests passed** against the running WildFly container\n- **WildFly 31.0.1.Final** starts in ~10 seconds and deploys the WAR successfully\n- **639 services** started, including all 5 MDBs, JPA, JSF (Mojarra 4.0.5), PrimeFaces 13.0.8, RESTEasy\n\n### Key Changes Made in This Session\n1. **Fixed `FetchType.EAGER`** on `Itinerary.java` and `Schedule.java` `@OneToMany` annotations to resolve `LazyInitializationException`\n2. **Removed `@Transactional`** from `UploadDirectoryScanner.java` (invalid on EJB `@Singleton` beans)\n3. **Fixed Dockerfile** - Added `ENTRYPOINT []` to reset the base image's Open Liberty entrypoint, and switched to JSON-form CMD for WildFly\n\n### Errors Resolved (Total: 10)\nAll errors from compilation through runtime were identified, diagnosed, and fixed iteratively:\n- Dependency issues (Jackson, ConnectionFactory, EntityManager, FacesContext)\n- JPA lazy loading (2 `@OneToMany` collections)\n- EJB annotation conflict (`@Transactional` on `@Singleton`)\n- Docker entrypoint override (Open Liberty vs WildFly)\n- WildFly CLI configuration issues (H2 driver, password)\n\n### Documentation\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md` including all files changed, errors encountered, and resolutions.","session_id":"be751ba2-32a8-49a7-8b94-68e2cc55da12","total_cost_usd":36.86473445999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":161,"cache_creation_input_tokens":451118,"cache_read_input_tokens":13151046,"output_tokens":53039,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":451118}},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":798,"outputTokens":25822,"cacheReadInputTokens":708108,"cach